## Welcome to the "Hello World" of platformOS!

Following the steps in the sidebar navigation will take you from setting up your development environment to deploying your first platformOS site.

After you get access to the Partner Portal, following and finishing the tutorials in this section should take less than half an hour.

Each step includes tips for learning more: recommendations for further reading, links to our glossary and an in-depth explanation of concepts you might not be familiar with.
